headline: Is PulteGroup (PHM) Pricing Reflect Strong Housing Momentum Or Leave Further Room To Run
summary: If you are wondering whether PulteGroup's current share price lines up with its underlying worth, you are not alone. This article is built to help you frame that question clearly. PulteGroup shares last closed at US$132.87, with returns of 7.9% over the past week, 6.8% over the past month, 11.6% year to date, 14.5% over one year and very large gains of around 2x over three and five years.
